channel.title: Something I Can Offer, No Other Place Can?
channel.description:
That's what I need. Knowing me, as an eFriend, what do you think I can do, or create, that no other forum or site has.
It needs to be something big. I'm very happy to do weeks of research. I just need something, that I'm capable of, and being able to release it.
It can't be RuneScape related, it can't be P Server related.
Many thanks <3

item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

[quote=“Mr.Chris, post:10, topic:53415”]Actually, reviews on games, and technology have been a point I’ve tried to involve in the previous forum.

The only thing with Graphics, is that there are so many Graphics communities out there, and my one would be nothing special.

I have 40GBs of storage space, and unlimited MySQL DBs. Space isn’t a problem.[/quote]

That’s what I mean, a forum for everything to do with computers, you could have graphic sections, games, hardware, software, operating systems, tech talk and a lot more. In my opinion it has the best chances of getting unique visitors, because it could expand on so many topics that someone looking for say pokemon cheats could find a forum for everything else + pokemon cheats.
